"v.伴随，陪伴 【英】 v. 伴随,陪伴(walk with sb as a companion ) 【记】 ac+company(伙伴, 公司); 【同】 派生词: accompaniment (n.伴随物; [音]伴奏); accompanist (n.伴奏者) v. 伴随, 陪伴(作为同伴相处或同行); 为...伴奏 【例】Please accompany me on the trip to my hometown 请陪我去故乡走一走. I accompanied he on the piano 我弹琴给他伴奏. 【记】ac朝...方向, company同伴, 公司 【参】accompaniment(n 伴随物; [音]伴奏); accompanist(n 伴奏者) 【记】源自companion 同伴, 共事者；company 公司是一群员工组成 accompany (v.)  early 15c., ""to be in company with,"" from Middle French accompagner, from Old French acompaignier (12c.) ""take as a companion,"" from à ""to"" (see ad-) + compaignier, from compaign (see companion). Related: Accompanied; accompanying."
